# Pin installs to the PUBLIC npm registry. The default global config on dev
# machines points at the corporate JFrog Artifactory (icseng.jfrog.io), which a
# GitHub-hosted CI runner can't authenticate to (401) — and the lockfile would
# otherwise bake those private URLs in. All deps here are public open-source
# packages, so resolve them straight from npm.
registry=https://registry.npmjs.org/
